From e8d026548e88221580cbaeb7a8906bced0295402 Mon Sep 17 00:00:00 2001
From: Akshay Ragir <akshay.ragir@ittiam.com>
Date: Thu, 12 Oct 2023 12:41:06 +0530
Subject: [PATCH] Fix for the Index-out-of-bounds in iusace_quantize_lines

These changes handle the index-out-of-bounds runtime error
reported when the bit consumption exceeds the bit reservoir
and global gain reaches the maximum value. The issue is
reported with USAC and the same changes are extended to AAC.

Bug: ossFuzz: 63019
Test: poc in bug
---
